==English==
===Etymology===
Thought to be from [[Doll]] (short for [[Dorothy]]) rather than from [[doll]]
===Intransitive verb===
'''to [[doll]] [[up]]'''
# to [[dress]] oneself in [[formal]] or [[ostentatious]] [[clothing]] as if for a [[special]] [[occasion]]
#:''She's all '''dolled up''' and nowhere to go.''